%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^GREEN%^Plague Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Unseen before rise of civilizations, plague domain blends together response nature gave societies created by the races.

Clerics with the Plague Domain gain the following benefits:
- Immunity to disease.

The plague domain contains the following spells:

Touch Of Sickening, Necrophage, Contagion, Purge Spirit, Greater Contagion, Epidemic, Plague Storm, Horrid Wilting, Entropic Storm

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nilith, Nimnavanon

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
